    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This vehicle exhibits exceptional mechanical fidelity, with a recently serviced dual-VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides precise shift gates, while the factory limited-slip differential remains tight and responsive. The suspension maintains original geometry with no bushing deflection, and the engine pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline with perfect compression. A truly turn-key, high-performance chassis for the discerning purist.",
