      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a true showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior features original factory paint with a deep, glass-like luster, completely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Every panel alignment is factory-perfect. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery shows no bolster wear or creasing, and the carpets have been protected by original floor mats since day one. All interior electronics, including the high-fidelity sound system and navigation, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with full documentation included. The engine bay is detailed and spotless, the transmission shifts with factory-new precision, and the undercarriage is free of any corrosion. This vehicle has never seen inclement weather and has been adult-owned and smoke-free. For the discerning buyer seeking a collector-grade example that drives as perfectly as it looks, this car is unparalleled.",
